org.usb4java

Class SsUsbDeviceCapabilityDescriptor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.usb4java.SsUsbDeviceCapabilityDescriptor

  • public final class SsUsbDeviceCapabilityDescriptor
extends Object
    A structure representing the SuperSpeed USB Device Capability descriptor. This descriptor is documented in section 9.6.2.2 of the USB 3.0 specification. All multiple-byte fields are represented in host-endian format.
    Author:
    Klaus Reimer (k@ailis.de)

    • Constructor Summary

      Constructors 
      Constructor and Description
      SsUsbDeviceCapabilityDescriptor()
      Constructs a new SuperSpeed USB Device Capability descriptor which can be passed to the LibUsb.getSsUsbDeviceCapabilityDescriptor(Context, BosDevCapabilityDescriptor, SsUsbDeviceCapabilityDescriptor) method.
